g.text: Divide the problem into sub problem solve it individually and combine the result.
Sn stands for sub problem solution, can be run parallel.
S stands for combine of sub problem solution
Follows local optimal choice at each stage with intend of finding global optimum
Optimal Solution :- Minimal cost, maximum profit, low risk
Dynamic programming :- It's divide the problem into series of overlapping sub problems.
Con's :- May or may not given optimal solution.
